        Enables UNMAP/TRIM on Clusters-1,2,3
        Set-AVSVSANClusterUNMAPTRIM -Enable:True
        Enables UNMAP/TRIM on all Clusters
    .PARAMETER Enable
        Set to true to enable UNMAP/TRIM on target cluster(s). Default is false.
